precis:
Amendments to the FISH INSPECTION REGULATIONS which increase existing
fees and establish new fees for fish inspection services, and authorize
the Minister to cancel or refuse to issue import licences and to suspend
registration certificates for serious breaches of the Regulations or
non-payment of fees.
